00:38:05,112 --> 00:38:06,592
The Hermit Duck's image

354
00:38:07,592 --> 00:38:09,072
is restrained and disciplined.

355
00:38:10,232 --> 00:38:11,632
It reminds me of myself.

356
00:38:14,353 --> 00:38:15,672
So when I saw this pendant,

357
00:38:15,913 --> 00:38:16,993
I immediately wanted it.

358
00:38:17,793 --> 00:38:18,632
I remember

359
00:38:19,672 --> 00:38:21,873
