360
00:38:22,152 --> 00:38:23,393
And I snatched it right off.

361
00:38:38,393 --> 00:38:40,232
Still no news about your sister?

362
00:38:47,353 --> 00:38:48,473
I'll find her.

363
00:38:50,152 --> 00:38:50,953
